    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you enact this plan as an action, you prepare yourself for every form of attack. For the next hour, your Defense bonus is +3.</p><hr /><p><strong>Level 5:</strong> The bonus becomes +4. While this plan is active, you can use this bonus in place of your Strength or Dexterity modifier when making a saving throw.</p><p><strong>Level 9:</strong> The bonus becomes +5.</p>",
